    desc: 'Steps from the calm waters of the Vecgauja — perfect for morning walks, kayaking, and fishing.',
  },
  {
    icon: '🌲',
    title: 'National Park Access',
    desc: 'The Carnikava protected coastal area starts right outside. Pine forest trails from the garden.',
  },
  {
    icon: '🏖️',
