    desc: '2 km walk through the national park forest brings you to an unspoiled stretch of Baltic coastline.',
  },
  {
    icon: '🏡',
    title: 'Private Garden',
    desc: 'A generous private garden with outdoor seating — ideal for summer evenings and morning coffee.',
